        <p style="font-size:18px;color:#999;line-height:1.6;">In 2026, OFM agencies no longer have the luxury of choosing a CRM for onsite work alone. Off-platform — Telegram, WhatsApp, alternative processors — has become the real playing field. Here is the honest comparison between the two most-used tools.</p>
